<p class="ql-align-right">芒果培优 | 红人计划 | 练习生 | 训练生 | 学员 | 采访</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">MANGO EDUCATION</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200929/ebc8789e92d7476cb988da804ec19be7.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>旅游狂人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>密室“坦克”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>极限运动爱好者</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>悬疑剧迷、清纯甜妹</strong>……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这些tag都属于<strong>林金熙</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200929/1abdb9f9c47843d9b2bac4b61c780b8b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>#反 差 萌 斜 杠 少 女#</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200929/6775de706d8f4013b0f4e17d2cdb90bb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
